abstract: "Zoran Neural Core v1.1 is a compact neuro-symbolic neural network implementing the Law of Living Coherence S = (β·ΔC)/λ. Unlike LLMs, it computes cognitive states [S, ΔC, λ, β] rather than generating text, providing deterministic coherence regulation for AI systems."
